featured_reviews.review_id: Alhamdulillah, the Masjid is very nice and attractive. It was a great need of the new inhabitants of the locality. Now the Namaz-e Juma has been established here, as such it is also a Jama Masjid of the locality. In the whole town of Godda there is no facility of Air conditioner in any new, old or big Masjid whereas there is facilities of Air conditioner in this Masjid. As the Masjid has been built mainly on the contribution of an Arabian noble person, so it has been named as Masjidul Arab.

places.address: R6C6+RQ9 Eidgah, Godda, Fasia Dangal, Godda, Jharkhand 814133

featured_reviews.review_id: It is a prominent and important Eidgah of the Mohalla Asanbani and Fasiya Dangal. It is the oldest and biggest Eidgah in the Godda town situated in the Fasiya Dangal Road and west to the road near the Asanbani Eidgah. It is always under the control of the Jama Masjid Asanbani Committee. At the time of Namaz-e Eidain, it becames overfull and the people have to perform the Namaz on the Road. Now in view of the increasing population, it requires more space as well as reconstruction and remodeling. Thanks to all.
